Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.09,0:00:05.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Halloween?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:06.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Halloween!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.86,0:00:09.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your place sells Japanese sweets...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.31,0:00:11.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's got nothing to do with Halloween.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:16.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, we decided to hold a fair and make Western-style Japanese sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.66,0:00:18.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then those are Western sweets...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:20.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:28.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, they're already made, and the fair is tomorrow, so I was thinking maybe you could come try some?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:30.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After school maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.44,0:00:32.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.38,0:00:34.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:36.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really something, so look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.24,0:00:37.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tamura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:39.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.23,0:00:47.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wondering for a while, but are you and Tamura-san going out?{Ulterior motives? Homoge?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:49.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Do we look like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:51.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:53.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I can't see it any other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:56.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not how we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.17,0:00:58.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're close of course, considering how long we've known each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.04,0:01:03.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're saying there aren't any feelings beyond that between you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.54,0:01:07.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.53,0:01:08.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Akagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.49,0:01:13.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's say for example you had a very kind old Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.88,0:01:16.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's this totally unrelated example coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.56,0:01:22.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, that Grandma gets magically transformed into a 15-year-old girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.61,0:01:28.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How would you feel about her, keeping in mind that she practically raised you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.15,0:01:32.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can imagine how I'd feel in such a messed up situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:35.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're pretty much like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.33,0:01:36.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You lost me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:40.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't really care if you understand or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:46.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, you're not going out, and you never intend to?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.99,0:01:48.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you asking me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:54.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So if some guy made a move on her, you wouldn't care?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:56.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I would!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.23,0:01:57.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'd allow that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:02:01.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd beat the crap out of anyone messed up enough to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.13,0:02:03.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So basically...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:06.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's nothing more than a childhood friend to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.88,0:02:08.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going out with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.68,0:02:10.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no feelings for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.47,0:02:14.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you wouldn't allow any other guys to go out with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.84,0:02:16.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.30,0:02:19.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So what did you do last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:21.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:01.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:03.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home. {good song}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:05.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A package arrived for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:13.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:15.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A dakimakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:20.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... something I found online that relieves stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:21.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:24.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it works, let me know. {Yeah. Tired. Right.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.65,0:04:25.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:32.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't let her know... {even though it's going on your bed?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.81,0:04:49.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... sure is Halloween.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:51.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to get customers with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:53.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:55.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing an event for the first day too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:56.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Event?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:05:01.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to invite the kids from around the neighborhood and show them how to make sweets and hand them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:05.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The workers are going to be dressed up as monsters too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:06.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:08.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean your Grandparents?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:12.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of the family too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:14.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll be help—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:16.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:19.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:21.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, you okay??
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.58,0:05:22.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:24.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:28.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Call an ambulance, Manami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:28.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!! {yeah, let's just toss the possible corpse around}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.19,0:05:35.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.49,0:05:39.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Kyou-chan. Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:41.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma!! Grandpa has...{FOTC: Consistency: Gramps or Grandpa?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:42.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:45.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's playing dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:48.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No wait, he really is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:50.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,His body's gone cold already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.02,0:05:54.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He got into the shop refrigerator a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:58.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what it was for...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:06:01.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But he doesn't have a pulse!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.43,0:06:04.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always had a weak pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:09.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does he smell like a corpse? {why do you know what a corpse smells like?}{Obviously someone made a pass at Manami.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.27,0:06:10.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's his natural body odor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.69,0:06:13.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But... wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:21.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, if you don't cut it out, I'll pull the hairs out of your head one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.92,0:06:29.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dang, you're one devil of a wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.67,0:06:33.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you even think of harming what little hair I have left?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:35.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.71,0:06:39.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy Halloween, Kyou-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:42.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Trick or... what was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.19,0:06:44.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Has your brain started to rot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.94,0:06:46.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:48.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the number for an ambulance??
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:49.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:54.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you're still alive, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:55.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.19,0:06:59.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a little carried away...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.45,0:07:02.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to punch him in the face!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:03.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Kyou-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:07.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you playing dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:10.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just practicing my costume for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:13.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My zombie impression was great, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:16.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, you seemed more like a normal corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:19.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Any kid who sees you will get traumatized.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:21.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you should let them see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.78,0:07:25.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:31.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:32.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well fine then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:34.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like I care anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.67,0:07:37.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother consoling him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:40.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you play along with him he'll just go overboard again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.74,0:07:41.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:46.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get some of the Halloween candy then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:49.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:54.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be popular with the grannies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:55.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't make me happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:56.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And why was that plural?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:00.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you done it yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:01.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Done what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:02.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And of course we haven't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:05.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's An-chan! Been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:06.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, long time—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:08.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:09.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I cut it all off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:10.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.66,0:08:12.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Skinheads are popular nowadays!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:15.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a monk's buzzcut, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:17.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No skinhead looks like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:20.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, An-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:26.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The barber said, "Right, skinhead. Skinhead."\Nthen cut it with his clipper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:29.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He even asked how short I wanted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:31.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a totally different hairstyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:34.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to use a special razor for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.25,0:08:35.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I know much about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:36.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.38,0:08:37.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That barber ripped me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:41.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:43.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since you came back with that I've been wanting to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:44.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no "skin" there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:46.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,for the longest time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:48.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have just told him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:54.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You cut your hair on a whim so you got what's coming to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.64,0:08:56.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Rock! {is this what it's supposed to be?}{FOTC: Yeah.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:08:58.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rock"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:09:00.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, get this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.19,0:09:01.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When he got back from the barber he was all like,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:08.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Check out my awesome hairstyle! From now on you can call me Rock!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:09.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name's Iwao though...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:11.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tamura Iwao...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:16.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Adults are all liars! {Some good angst there.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:19.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't trust those over-50s! {That's a good one.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.82,0:09:24.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,These are really elaborate...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:26.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:34.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please go ahead and try some!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.86,0:09:37.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:50.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:51.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.47,0:09:54.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You put actual pumpkin inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:09:56.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:58.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you make these?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:01.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:03.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you wanted to know what I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:06.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I made them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.28,0:10:08.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you like them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.80,0:10:12.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:15.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you two just get married already?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:17.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:21.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes even he makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:24.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, stop that you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:26.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou-chan, let's go to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.86,0:10:28.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:34.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Woo! Getting hot up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:37.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so old...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:37.15,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:56.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:57.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to hide something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:10:58.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.71,0:11:04.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess this isn't {\i1}her{\i0} we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that??{Kirino yandere end too?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:23.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! {like she'd buy a non ero one...}{This is why I don't open the package.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.19,0:11:39.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's really changed here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:40.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop staring!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.93,0:11:41.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It‘s embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:49.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:53.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:57.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've been staying up late studying too much these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:12:00.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like just relaxing and taking a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:00.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:03.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what you meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:05.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No studying allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:07.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I even left my textbooks at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:08.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:10.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just relax then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.32,0:12:13.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:14.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,‘Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:26.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you need to help prepare for the fair?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:29.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but that'll be after the shop closes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.11,0:12:32.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole family will be working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:33.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lend a hand then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:34.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.89,0:12:36.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be a great help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:39.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:40.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:42.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:43.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.48,0:12:47.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not exactly payment, but you can have dinner here then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:51.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, a tea stalk is standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:52.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, neat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:05.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah, this is heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:08.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:19.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:22.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,An-chan, I understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:24.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock isn't how you look...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:25.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a way of life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:29.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's little difference between a skinhead and a short buzz!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.21,0:13:31.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, I shout with all my soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:34.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And why are you playing a shamisen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:36.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's more like a biwa player than a rocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:38.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have a guitar—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:42.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:43.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.88,0:13:51.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:55.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, Kyou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:13:59.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... do you want dinner first or a bath first?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:01.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:08.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since you visited, so Grandpa and Grandma and Dad said you should stay over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.02,0:14:09.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:16.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa and Grandma and Dad are really happy to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:18.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa's—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:20.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa and Grandma—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:21.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gra—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:23.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa had Grandma—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:26.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, I'll sleep over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:27.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.73,0:14:29.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.17,0:14:30.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:37.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long since you slept over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:38.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:40.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to come over all the time too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.18,0:14:43.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be because, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:49.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're that age now, so you get nervous staying at a girl's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.93,0:14:53.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I get nervous staying at your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:54.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:55.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.90,0:14:58.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more relaxing here than at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.26,0:15:00.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:01.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:07.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, I just thought it might be better that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.54,0:15:25.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:28.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's staying at the Tamuras'.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:30.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, he's always acting like a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.77,0:15:32.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you talk to the parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:34.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:36.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They said it'd help with their Halloween.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:37.81,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Halloween?{Dad}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:37.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food. {Kirino}{FOTC: How do we do itadakimasu?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:38.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.{Mom}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:43.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:53.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,An-chan, how do you play a C minor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:55.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any chords on a shamisen, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:16:00.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou-chan, Dad's about to get out of the bath. Do you want to take one next?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.03,0:16:02.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can go last. You take one first.{And drink that delicious bathwater.}{http://fotc.ath.cx/images/121488582250.jpg} {why do you have that on hand....}{Because it's good.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.95,0:16:05.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine going after you.{And drink that delicious bathwater.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:06.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you take one first.{And drink that delicious bathwater.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:20.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about taking one together?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:25.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou-chan, you're blushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.45,0:16:29.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's take one together!{Pro SFX}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:33.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:34.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Super serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.75,0:16:36.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You already invited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:38.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't take it back now, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:41.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,An-chan, you're a real man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:43.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:45.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Manami!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:49.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you my hyper-weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:55.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma, what do I do??
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.48,0:16:58.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou-chan wants to take a bath with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:16:59.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go telling everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.78,0:17:01.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So take one with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.34,0:17:03.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—it was a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:05.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You so want to, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:06.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:17.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:23.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:25.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:28.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I put your futon in your usual room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:29.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:31.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll sleep then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.10,0:17:34.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go back to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:35.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:36.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach me how to play this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.85,0:17:37.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:39.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:41.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:44.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How many years has it been since we were up until bedtime together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:46.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Four years, I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:52.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.99,0:17:54.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:01.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou-chan! Kyou-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:03.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My futon is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:05.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? My futon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:06.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:09.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why is it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:11.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And right next to yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:14.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do this, Kyou-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:15.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:17.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:19.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Analyze the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:22.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so basically... I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.37,0:18:24.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou-chan, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.71,0:18:27.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.03,0:18:28.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.22,0:18:33.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little something with my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:43.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you doing, Grandpa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:46.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's trauma from the War.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:52.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't sleep there with Manami, my chest gets wracked with pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:53.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of trauma causes that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.97,0:18:56.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:58.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma's calling for me from across the River Styx...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:18:59.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:01.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma's downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:02.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:04.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't sleep together at our age!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:05.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.65,0:19:07.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:10.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:12.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.54,0:19:16.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:18.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Wait, you damn nutjob!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:38.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like we're kids again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:43.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We used to sleep like this all the time back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:46.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought we'd do it at this age.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.42,0:19:48.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all that old codger's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:51.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And Grandma... maybe some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:54.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:55.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.70,0:19:59.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night, Kyou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.65,0:20:09.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Still awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:11.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Still awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.17,0:20:13.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.22,0:20:17.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice if we went to the same college.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:19.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.77,0:20:27.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how things'll be if we graduate and go to the same college.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.09,0:20:28.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How what will be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:29.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.47,0:20:34.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it'll change much.{FOTC: I don't think they'll change much.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:37.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:40.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Manami...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:41.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:46.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What if someone told you they liked you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.87,0:20:47.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:49.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.55,0:20:50.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"What if"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:52.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hypothetical!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.84,0:20:56.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of fantastic guy might never appear!{FOTC: It's not like that kind of messed up guy might never appear!}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.70,0:21:01.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If... I don't know what if.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:04.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Figured...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.02,0:21:06.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:09.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.59,0:21:12.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone told you they liked you, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:20.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd turn them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.23,0:21:22.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.11,0:21:26.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I like leading a peaceful life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.50,0:21:28.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are fine the way they are right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.71,0:21:32.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Being able to relax in this kind of home is enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.46,0:21:35.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.34,0:21:41.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We've still got a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.38,0:21:42.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Spoken like a true Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:45.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're talking like a Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:53.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:54.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.94,0:21:57.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... er...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.93,0:22:00.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.56,0:22:01.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.74,0:22:06.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to come to my place next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.57,0:22:08.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.90,0:22:12.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'd like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.90,0:22:14.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometime soon then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.93,0:22:16.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.19,0:22:17.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.85,0:22:19.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times is that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.71,0:22:20.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.55,0:22:30.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, don't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.34,0:22:34.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.25,0:24:06.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Comment: 0,0:24:06.24,0:24:09.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's No Way My Childhood Friend Could Be This Cute
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:33.00,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,そんな優しくしないで　どんな顔すればいいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:36.30,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,積み重ねた言葉で　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:41.80,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,見えないよ　きみの横顔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:55.52,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,どこだっけ？　なくした鍵は見つからないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:03:02.28,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,ため息...すれ違いに意地張って疲れちゃう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:08.91,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,ほんの少し近く　きみとの距離が
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:16.08,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,うまく掴めないんだ　あとちょっとなのに!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.08,0:03:23.26,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,そんな優しくしないで　ほら　また傷つけあって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:30.10,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,積み重ねたウソでもう　動けなくなってる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:37.57,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,すぐに会いに行きたいけど　言葉は見つからないし
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:47.79,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,最後の一ページかい　きみには笑顔見せたい
Comment: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:49.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Romaji}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:33.00,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,sonna yasashiku shinai de donna kao sureba ii no?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:36.30,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,tsumikasaneta kotoba de
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:41.80,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,mienai yo kimi no yokogao
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:55.52,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,dokodakke? nakushita kagi ha mitsukaranai mama de
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:03:02.28,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,tameiki... surechigai ni iji hatte tsukarechau
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:08.91,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,hon no sukoshi chikaku kimi to no kyori ga
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:16.08,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,umaku tsukamenainda ato chotto na no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.08,0:03:23.26,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,sonna yasashikushinaide hora mata kizutsukeatte
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:30.10,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,tsumikasaneta uso demo ugokenakunatteru
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:37.57,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,sugu ni ai ni ikitai kedo kotoba ha mitsukaranai shi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:47.79,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,saigo no ichi pe-ji kurai kimi ni ha egao misetai
Comment: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:24.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Translation}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:32.96,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so nice to me, I just don't know how to react
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:36.26,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,With all these words piling up,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:41.76,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even see your face
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:55.48,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it? I lost my key, now I can't find it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:03:02.24,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Sigh, I'll burn out if I keep acting like this whenever we fight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:08.87,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we're close? I just can't figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:16.08,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how far away I am, even though you're right there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.08,0:03:23.26,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so nice to me, see? We hurt each other again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:30.10,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,With all these lies piling up, I can't even move
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:37.53,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you now, but I don't know what to say
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:47.74,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is the end for our story, I want you to see my smile
Comment: 0,0:24:09.32,0:24:09.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.95,0:22:53.62,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,長く近くにいると　見えなくなるもの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.94,0:23:00.00,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,いつかどこかで見つけて　私は変わった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.00,0:23:05.64,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,ねぇ　あなたは変わらないね　だからもどかしいの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.97,0:23:12.64,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,でも多分　そう言うとこ含めて　好きなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.64,0:23:17.54,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,また二人で変えて行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.54,0:23:23.64,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,ずっとこんな関係が　続けばいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.01,0:23:31.46,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,急に寸だ　このマエガミみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:37.08,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,目覚めた想いが　もう戻らないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.48,0:23:43.92,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,地味な私だけど　そのままでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:51.30,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,あなたの言葉　熱く熱く残っている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.95,0:22:53.62,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,nagaku chikaku ni iru to mienakunaru mono
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.94,0:23:00.00,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,itsuka dokoka de mitsukete watashi ha kawatta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.00,0:23:05.64,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,nee anata ha kawaranai ne dakara modokashii no
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.97,0:23:12.64,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,demo tabun sou iu toko fukumete suki nanda
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.64,0:23:17.54,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,mata futari de kaeteyuku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.54,0:23:23.64,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,zutto konna kankei ga tsudzukeba ii no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.01,0:23:31.46,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,kyuu ni sunda kono maegami mitai ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:37.08,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,mezameta omoi ga mou modoranai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.48,0:23:43.92,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,jimi na watashi dakedo sono mama de ii
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:51.30,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,anata no kotoba atsuku atsuku nokotteiru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.95,0:22:53.62,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,When you’ve been together for so long, sometimes you just forget about it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.94,0:23:00.00,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometime, somewhere, I found it, but I had changed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.00,0:23:05.64,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you never seem to change, that’s why I’m so upset
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.97,0:23:12.64,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think that’s part of what I like about you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.64,0:23:17.54,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll just keep changing together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.54,0:23:23.64,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it would be so nice to stay like this forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.01,0:23:31.46,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like my bangs that I suddenly cut short
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:37.08,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,My feelings all came up, now I can’t go back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.48,0:23:43.92,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,I might be so plain, but that’s all okay
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:51.30,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you said still warms me deep inside
